d>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">060886770619</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FLEXIBLE RUBBER SLUICE MAT: Once your material is run through the mat it can easily be rolled up letting you rinse out the concentrate that you have trapped; Made from TPR rubber that will not stiffen in cold weather</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">3 RIFFLE TRAP PATTERNS: There are 3 different pattern gold collection riffle traps allow for various sizes of gold material to be trapped while each serving a different purpose to help aid in the gold prospecting recovery process</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HUNGARIAN: Increases the turbulence behind the riffle, which agitates the sand bed, improving gold deposits; V-SHAPE: these groves work very well for catching fine gold flake; SQUARE RIFFLE: The large groves allow for catching small finds, pickers, and small gold nuggets</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">CUT TO FIT: The sluice box matting is pre-scored so it can easily be cut down to only 8 inches wide using the guide line on the back of the matting. Overall dimensions of the matting are 10 inches wide by 27 inches in length</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">MAXIMIZE RECOVERY EFFORTS: This is the perfect mat for superb fine gold recovery with fast or slow water and will enhance your gold prospecting and recovery efforts</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor Rubber Riffled Gold Sluice Box Matting for Gold Recovery, 27x10 inch</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">49.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>The ASR Outdoor Rubber Riffle Sluice Box Mat is made from highly durable, one-piece flexible rubber that will never harden or crack in cold weather and is designed with 3 traditional, tried and true fine gold collecting riffle patterns. These gold recovery riffle traps are designed to maximize the amount of gold nuggets and gold flake that is trapped when separated from your raw screened material. \n\nThis Rubber Riffled Sluice Box Matting is manufactured from green thermoplastic rubber (TPR) allowing for optimal clarity and easy spotting and identifying of gold flake, gold nuggets, gems, or your choice rock hounding mineral. It is also a Trimmable Riffle Sluice Box Matting which is pre-scored so it can easily be cut down to only 8 inches wide using the guide line on the back of the matting. Overall dimensions of the matting are 10 inches wide by 27 inches in length; with riffle traps running the entire length.\n\nThis is the perfect sluice box mat for superb fine gold recovery with fast or slow water which will enhance your gold prospecting and recovery efforts.\n\nThe different pattern gold collection riffle traps allow for various sizes of material to be trapped while each serving a different purpose to help aid in the gold prospecting recovery process;  they are; Hungarian, V-shape, and Square riffle patterns;\n\n<b>Hungarian Riffle Trap:</b> Increases the turbulence behind the riffle, which agitates the sand bed, improving gold deposits within the recovery traps\n<b>V Shape Riffle Trap:</b> V-shaped groves work very well for catching fine gold\n<b>Square Riffle Trap:</b> The large groves allow for catching small finds, pickers, and small nuggets\n\nOnce your gold pay dirt material is run through the mat it can easily be rolled up to let you rinse out the concentrate that you have trapped. The concentrate rinsed from the matting will contain most of the gold accumulated during the run and is now ready to be panned and separated.\n\nThese traditional and proven riffle patterns will help increase the amount of gold and minerals you recover. Always sift or screen your material first using the ASR Outdoor Classifier Sifter Screens to ensure that your gold prospecting material that is run through your sluice box matting is finely separated from your raw material, maximizing your efficiency in the field.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026</p></div></div>",
